OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and very warm to hot day
OL,6,Fwith hazy sunshine to the north,
OL,7,Fbrighter spells further south. A
OL,8,Fgentle breeze strengthens slightly
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon before easing
OL,10,Flight by the evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry start to the night but
OL,13,Fclouding over with outbreaks of rain
OL,14,Fin places during the second half. The
OL,15,Fwind remains light for most.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FAny rain should quickly
OL,18,Fclear with sunny spells to follow.
OL,19,FSunshine turning a little hazy by the
OL,20,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
